      "text": "こころ達が歌を届ける相手をよく知ることが出来たし\n北海道の人も風景も、前よりずっと好きになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to get to know the people we're singing for better‚\nAnd I like the people and scenery of Hokkaido much more than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.8847349806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
